Then go to the fourth again.

36:15.580 --> 36:16.790
- Okay,
but wait, wait, wait.

36:16.790 --> 36:18.500
"You were on
the tip of my tongue."

36:18.500 --> 36:20.290
I like that, but then...

36:20.290 --> 36:22.420
Yeah, um...
Let's do it again.

36:22.420 --> 36:24.460
In your...
