You could just say,

36:40.080 --> 36:42.080
all this time I waited...

36:42.080 --> 36:44.250
I want it
to really feel honest.

36:44.250 --> 36:46.460
- I know, and it's about me
at that point anyway, right?

36:46.460 --> 36:49.420
- Well, I'm trying to say
that I had a part in it, too.

36:49.420 --> 36:51.790
( both laugh )

36:54.380 --> 36:56.920
In the wind, you were on
the tip of my tongue.

36:57.920 --> 37:00.170
- Like a kiss on my cheek.

37:00.170 --> 37:01.880
- Yeah.

37:03.710 --> 37:04.960
- Yeah, that's it.

